{"tid":1819962,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【代post】Hktvmall TG 前任admin  近況及澄清","createTime":"2020-01-11T09:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T15:36:42.000Z","uid":275471,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6ecdd0ddaf40f5f43ef7b3b39b0323ebe4778fe3","tid":1819962,"uid":275471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"大家好 <br />\n我係hktvmall前admin <br />\nTG ID:Hkfreedom2019<br />\n以家已經係一個被捕人士<br />\n而我以家可能受既刑期 係十年以上<br />\n案件現而進入調查階段<br />\n我唔自爆自己邊日被捕同咩罪名喇<br />\n<br />\n但我想澄清返 由出事到現在<br />\n我除左法律支援外 我冇受過任何援助<br />\n我搞到今日既處境 <br />\n全因爲我想保護自己身邊既人<br />\n我亦唔後悔<br />\n我從來冇篤過任何人既灰<br />\n因為我地係一個正當既人道代購組織<br />\n<br />\n而我係一直用緊自己既儲蓄<br />\n除左法律資源外<br />\n以前又好 以家又好<br />\n但我唔會亦唔需要任何人俾援助我<br />\n我仲有手有腳可以搞掂自己<br />\n如果家長有呢個意慾 <br />\n請向可信channel捐助<br />\n仲有好多冇求生技能既小朋友<br />\n比我更有需要<br />\n<br />\n我做過既所有野我唔後悔<br />\n無需要感謝我<br />\n我亦需要你地尊重我<br />\n但請唔好中傷我人格<br />\n如有任何證據 歡迎向我對質<br />\n<br />\n附下銀行statement 圖片<br />\nPS:我連Payme都俾人凍結埋<br />\n圖中包括我銀行現時狀況<br />\n入面既現金全部都用黎找計劃用既卡數<br />\n果時我total買左15萬既單<br />\n做左一年分期<br />\n而呢兩個月 我銀行除左薪金外<br />\n全部都係支出並冇收入<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sSeDbXb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsSeDbXb.jpg&h=2fc69869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YLZFQw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YLZFQw.jpg&h=0bb46612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYYDWoS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYYDWoS.jpg&h=247e5ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kT12DCc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkT12DCc.jpg&h=8ec8ea0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpQbwXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpQbwXd.jpg&h=6a3a87f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c86cd4e308388de588cd61ea45c7d64bfef61114","tid":1819962,"